Package ie.gmit.encode

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Encoder
    A interface abstracted basic behaviors of an Encoder
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEncoder
    An abstract class of an encoder, implements Encoder, base class of all other encoder classes.
    Base64Encoder
    Subclass of AbstractEncoder, use an Adapter, implements Encoder.
    EncoderFactory
    Factory for generating different algorithms' encoders.
    FileEncoder
    Subclass of AbstractEncoder, implements Encoder.
    HuffmanEncoder
    Subclass of AbstractEncoder, use Huffman algorithm, implements Encoder.
    HuffmanLeaf
    Defines HuffmanLeaf in a HuffmanTree, subclass of HuffmanUnit.
    HuffmanNode
    Defines HuffmanNode in a HuffmanTree, subclass of HuffmanUnit.
    HuffmanTree
    HuffmanTree used to store and sort HuffmanUnit(can either be HuffmanLeaf or HuffmanNode).
    HuffmanUnit
    Abstract class of the Units in a HuffmanTree.
    LempelZivEncoder
    Subclass of AbstractEncoder, use Lempel-Ziv algorithm, implements Encoder.
    RunlengthEncoder
    Subclass of AbstractEncoder, use Run-length algorithm, implements Encoder.
    UriEncoder  
    URLEncoder
    Subclass of AbstractEncoder, implements Encoder.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommandException
    Exception caused by User Command used in the EncoderFactory.
    EncodeException
    Exception caused by Encode.
    FileException
    Exception caused by wrong file path.
    UriException
    Exception caused by wrong Uri.
    URLException
    Exception caused by wrong URL.
